title: Trailer Hitch Installation CURT 12080 on a Mazda CX 5
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 12080 Class 2 trailer hitch on a 2016 Mazda CX-5. 

Install Sheet - 
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/12080/installsheet/CM_12080_INS.PDF

Application Coverage:
2013 - 2016 Mazda CX-5

Special Notes:
***DO NOT EXCEED VEHICLE MANUFACTURER'S RECOMMENDED TOWING CAPACITY***
PERIODICALLY CHECK THIS RECEIVER HITCH TO ENSURE THAT ALL FASTENERS
ARE TIGHT AND THAT ALL STRUCTURAL COMPONENTS ARE SOUND.

Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
tags: CURT Trailer Hitch, Receiver Hitch, Mazda CX-5, how to install trailer hitch, receiver hitch install
